description:
"وقايتنا" تطبيق مغربي متنقل يسمح للهواتف المحمولة لمستعمليها برصد هواتف أخرى محاذية تستعمل نفس التطبيق، وبتقاسم رموز تعريف مشفرة ومجهولة عبر هذه الأجهزة.

على سبيل المثال، إذا كنتم بسوق تجاري ممتاز، وتواجدتم بالقرب من شخص يستعمل تطبيق "وقايتنا"، فإن هاتفيكما المحمولة ستتبادل رموز تعريف مشفرة ومجهولة، هذه الرموز يتم تخزينها محليا على مستوى هاتفك المحمول. ولا يتم تبادل أي معطى شخصي يمكن استعماله من أجلتحديد هويتكم أو مكان تواجدكم.

في الحالة التي تتأكد فيها إصابة مستعمل لهذا التطبيق بفيروس كورونا المستجد المسبب لمرض "كوفيد-19"، فإنه السلطات الصحية تطلب منه إرسال لائحة رموز التعريف المخزنة محليا على مستوى هاتفه المحمول إلى خادم معلوماتي مركزي، وذلك باستعمال واجهة التطبيق "إعادة نقل المعطيات". وهذا سيمكن من تحديد الأشخاص الذين كانوا متواجدين بالقرب من الشخص المصاب، وذلك عبر رسالة نصية قصيرة، وبالتالي من التكفل السريع بهم من أجل تفادي المضاعفات المحتملة المرتبطة بالمرض والحد من العدوى.

يتم استعمال التطبيق حصريا على مستوى التراب المغربي من أجل التصدي لانتشار جائحة فيروس كورونا المستجد "كوفيد-19"، على أن يتم سحبها من تطبيق " Apple Store " بعد الإعلان عن نهاية الجائحة.

إن معالجة المعطيات المضمنة بتطبيق "وقايتنا" تعتبر مطابقة لمقتضيات القانون المغربي رقم 09.08 المتعلق بحماية الأشخاص الذاتيين تجاه معالجة المعطيات ذات الطابع الشخصي وتم الترخيص لهذا التطبيق ببلادنا من قبل اللجنة الوطنية لمراقبة حماية المعطيات ذات الطابع الشخصي بموجب الرخصة رقم:

A-S-192-EUS/2020 - T-S-87-EUS/2020 du 10/05/2020""

description:
Ứng dụng Sổ sức khỏe điện tử là là ứng dụng trên nền tảng thiết bị điện tử của Bộ y tế giúp người dân Việt Nam biết và tự quản lý thông tin sức khỏe của bản thân. Chủ động trong việc phòng bệnh và chăm sóc sức khỏe bản thân. 

Với ứng dụng Sổ sức khỏe điện tử mỗi người dân sẽ có 1 quyển sổ y bạ sức khỏe cả đời được kết nối trực tiếp với Hệ thống Hồ sơ sức khỏe cá nhân của Bộ Y tế, tạo thuận lợi cho cán bộ y tế chẩn đoán và điều trị người bệnh giúp họ được chăm sóc sức khỏe toàn diện và liên tục, phát hiện bệnh sớm, điều trị kịp thời khi bệnh còn ở giai đoạn sớm mang lại hiệu quả điều trị cao, giảm bớt chi phí khám bệnh, chữa bệnh của mỗi người dân. 
Ứng dụng Sổ sức khỏe điện tử giúp cho nhân viên y tế thu thập thông tin, giảm ùn tắc ở các điểm tiêm vắc-xin, hạn chế khả năng lây nhiễm cho người dân khi đi lấy tiêm vắc-xin COVID-19, hỗ trợ kịp thời các vấn đề về sức khỏe cho người dân.

Với ứng dụng Sổ sức khỏe điện tử mỗi người dân Việt Nam đã tiêm chủng Vắc xin Covid 19 sẽ có 1 "Chứng nhận tiêm chủng" điện tử bằng mã QR, kèm theo giấy chứng nhận tiêm chủng vắc-xin COVID-19 theo quy định của Bộ y tế.

Sổ sức khỏe điện tử có các tiện ích chính:
- Tiện ích Đăng ký tiêm chủng: Đăng ký tiêm vắc-xin COVID-19
- Tiện ích Xác nhận tiêm chủng: Cung cấp thông tin có đồng ý tiêm vắc-xin COVID-19 hay không
- Tiện ích Phản ứng sau tiêm: Cung cấp các thông tin y tế về tình trạng sức khỏe, các triệu chứng xảy ra nếu có sau khi được tiêm phòng vắc-xin COVID-19.
- Tiện ích Chứng nhận tiêm chủng: Chứng nhận đã tiêm vắc-xin COVID-19
- Tiện ích Đặt khám: Đặt lịch khám tại Cơ sở y tế.
- Tiện ích Hồ sơ sức khỏe: Thông tin về Hồ sơ sức khỏe cá nhân

Ứng dụng được áp dụng tại Việt Nam.

Xem điều khoản sử dụng tại: 

https://sites.google.com/view/sosuckhoedientu-privacy-policy/home

----------------------------
Nếu gặp khó khăn trong quá trình cài đặt hay sử dụng ứng dụng Sổ sức khỏe điện tử, vui lòng liên hệ tổng đài 19009095 để được trợ giúp. Đội ngũ phát triển ứng dụng Sổ sức khỏe điện tử đang nỗ lực để ứng dụng ngày càng hoàn thiện hơn, phục vụ đất nước và người dân trong công tác phòng chống dịch bệnh COVID-19.

Alhosn is the official digital health platform for vaccinations in the UAE and more, developed in partnership with the Ministry of Health and Prevention and local health authorities. 

Leveraging advanced artificial intelligence (AI) technology, Alhosn delivers a user-friendly experience that provides up-to-date information and convenient access to a wide range of vaccines and more. 

The platform also offers personalized vaccination reminders, maintains a comprehensive vaccination record, and provides a secure method for sharing vaccination data with relevant authorities and more.

'Gray's Anatomy', the renowned classic anatomical book by Henry Gray was first published in 1858 and is considered by many to be one of the most iconic and significant medical books of all time. Gray's Anatomy is now available on the iPhone using the highest resolution images possible. (This version of Gray's Anatomy has been enhanced and specifically built for iOS)

This Student iPhone and iPod Touch Edition of Grays Anatomy includes:
* COMPLETE TEXT and SD ILLUSTRATIONS
* SCROLLABLE THUMBNAILS OF ALL 1247 ILLUSTRATIONS
* Easy Navigation
* Bookmarks
and more


We recommend this app for Doctors, Nurses, Students, Teachers and anyone who is interested in the wonder and complexity of the human body.

* Note: this application was not written by McDreamy and the illustrations in no way resemble any characters from the television show Grey's Anatomy ;)

Altibbi App - the innovative platform offering telemedicine consultation services to improve patient care and empower them with high-quality medical advice anytime, anywhere, allowing them to communicate with doctors effortlessly. 
Why Altibbi?

• Share Medical Reports: Attach your medical reports and share them with doctors to receive the best recommendations and medical consultations
• Personal Health Record: A guide allowing you to keep your personal health records and monitor previous medical diagnoses

Altibbi App Features:

• Privacy, security, and data confidentiality
• A trusted source for families: Providing important and reliable health information anytime






For a better, healthier life with Altibbi:
• Save time and effort: Access telemedicine consultations through your mobile phone
• Medical consultations: Easily receive medical consultations from the comfort of your home
• Avoid waiting in crisis: Organize your daily life and avoid long waiting times at the doctor's clinic

How to use Altibbi app:
To benefit from the medical services and consultations, simply follow these steps to use the app:
1. Register your phone number and receive a verification code to proceed
2. Choose the appropriate subscription to start accessing medical consultations. After selecting the subscription type, tap on "Continue" to proceed
3. Enter your card details to complete the payment process and agree to the terms and conditions for continued access
4. Choose a suitable payment method through the available network on your phone or in your country
5. Once the subscription process is successfully completed, you can enjoy all the benefits offered by Altibbi and start medical consultations

Join the #1 Pregnancy & Baby Tracker App that’s Trusted by Millions for Week-by-Week Guidance and Baby Tracking Tools.

What to Expect is the world’s best-known baby development and growth tracker app chosen by more than 15 million parents. We’re the parenting, infant and family planning brand, offering you a free all-in-one pregnancy and baby tracker app with thousands of medically accurate articles, daily pregnancy updates, expert baby growth tracking, and personalized parenting tips to help you nurture a healthy pregnancy, a thriving baby, and confident parenting.

Find guides for every step of your growing family’s journey—from starting a family and recognizing early signs of pregnancy to navigating motherhood, newborn care, and the baby and toddler years. Find support and connection with moms, parents, and parents-to-be throughout your pregnancy journey.

During Pregnancy

* Due Date Calculator that determines your due date based on last period, IVF transfer, conception, and ultrasound, while sharing fun facts about your baby
* Week-by-week pregnancy tracker with info about baby development, symptoms and family preparation tips
* Themed baby size comparisons, visual countdown and 3D videos showing baby development in utero week by week of pregnancy
* Helpful daily tips designed to support you at every stage
* Keep track of your bump, symptoms, pregnancy weight, kick counts, birth plan and memories with our My Journal tool
* Expert-reviewed articles on signs of labor, pregnancy symptoms, baby and mom’s health and helpful tips
* Registry Builder to help you with your baby list and registry
* Detailed pregnancy and baby product reviews and expert buying guides
* Expecting Twins? Learn about different types of twins and possible fetal positions
* Use the contractions counter to track the frequency and duration of contractions

After Baby’s Arrival

* Baby Tracker that lets you time and track baby’s feedings, log pump sessions, diaper changes, tummy time, and more
* Month-by-month and milestone tracker for each step of your baby’s life, from the newborn to the toddler stage
* Daily tips tailored  to your baby’s age, stage, your postpartum recovery, and your parenting journey
* Record your postpartum symptoms and medications 
* Informative videos and articles about sleep schedules, feeding tips, milestones, and baby’s growth and week-by-week development
* Medically reviewed articles and info about baby’s health, doctor’s appointments and vaccines
* Join community groups meet people with due dates in the same month, newborn care, mom’s health conditions, parenting styles and more

Family Planning

* Ovulation Calculator that pinpoints your most fertile days based on last period and cycle
* Due Date Calculator that helps you figure out baby’s potential due date when you’re trying to conceive (TTC)
* Ovulation tracker and early pregnancy signs, plus keep a journal of your feelings when you’re trying to get pregnant
* Expert advice and articles to help you understand your cycle, signs of ovulation and pregnancy, fertility issues, adoption and surrogacy, and more
* Community groups devoted to preparing for pregnancy and fertility treatments

About Us 

All content on the What to Expect app is accurate, up-to-date, and reviewed by medical experts, including the What to Expect Medical Review Board. It aligns with current health guidelines and Heidi Murkoff’s trusted books 

Medical information comes from expert sources like ACOG, AAP, CDC, and peer-reviewed journals to ensure reliability and credibility.

For more about What to Expect's medical review and editorial policy, visit: https://www.whattoexpect.com/medical-review/

app_name: 中医精华-经络穴位图解体检颈椎推拿正念冥想睡眠情绪平衡音乐
description:
中医是研究人体生理、病理以及疾病的诊断和防治等的一门学科。中医诞生于原始社会，春秋战国时期中医理论已基本形成，之后历代均有总结发展。
中医承载着中国古代人民同疾病作斗争的经验和理论知识，通过长期医疗实践逐步形成并发展成的医学理论体系。
中医学以阴阳五行作为理论基础，使用中药、针灸、推拿、按摩、食疗等多种治疗手段，使人体达到阴阳调和而康复。
中医APP将中医最精华的部分萃取出来，把人体经络穴位、传统中药以及中医药膳食谱结合起来，将中华传统医学发扬光大。
中医APP弘扬中华传统文化，把中国古代最经典的曲目列出来，提供播放和定时功能。
